	<small>Date read: 2012-11-18. How strongly I recommend it: <strong>6</strong>/10</small>
	<p>If you've read other books on how to write a great story, this probably won't hold much new for you. But this was my first book on this subject, and I loved it. Changed the way I pay attention to movies and novels. Makes me want to write a novel.</p>
