	<small>Date read: 2006-09-21. How strongly I recommend it: <strong>8</strong>/10</small>
	<p>Required reading for business-owners and investors. Shows how technology improves faster than people's ability to use it, so when someone says a technology is “not good enough”, add “yet” and prepare for disruption.</p>
